snippet.title: The ER: Patient Typhon (launch trailer)
snippet.description:
Steam page:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1336210/The_ER_Patient_Typhon/

Welcome to the ER, Saint Icaros, where the patients wake up with missing body parts. Your memory is a bit foggy because of the terrible accident. Lucky for you, our doctor has a wonder drug that will make you heal in no time. So, do as we say and stop wondering why there are never any visitors.
